summary: This is an email transmitting a batch of serialized FBI 302 interview reports (FD-302 forms) related to the Epstein investigation. The email itself is a cover note listing attached PDF files containing the interview summaries.
keyFacts: The document is an email dated April 23, 2020, transmitting a batch of FBI 302 reports.
The attached files are serialized under the case number 050D-NY-3027571.
The email indicates these are 302s 'serialized since the last batch we gave you,' suggesting ongoing investigative document production.
